WEBVTT


00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:02.980
Stand tall, feet shoulder width apart.

00:00:03.160 --> 00:00:04.759
Stagger your right foot back

00:00:04.760 --> 00:00:06.620
slightly deeper than heel to toe.

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:07.799
Bend at the ankles,

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:08.940
knees, and waist.

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:11.500
Your forearms should be placed on your thighs.

00:00:12.080 --> 00:00:12.919
Rock forward,

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:15.119
extending your right hand down to the ground

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:16.420
in front of your eyes.

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:19.060
Always keep your head and eyes up.

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:23.180
Heels, toes, knees, and hands should all be aligned.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:26.260
Your hips should be slightly higher than your head.

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.879
Your left hand should be under your chin

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:30.180
and ready for use.

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:31.839
This right handed,

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:34.719
run based stance helps develop comfort

00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:38.009
using a consistent, explosive position to start a play.
